America, the policyholder-owned company based in New York,
promoted  Deanna Mulligan  to president and said she will take
over as chief executive officer next year.  Guardianâ€™s board will appoint Mulligan, 47, CEO on July 1,
the insurer said today in an e-mailed statement. On Nov. 1, CEO
